    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131290/extras/a2852297ac649dfd84850803fec3ab90.avif?t=1770154804\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131290/extras_big/a2852297ac649dfd84850803fec3ab90.avif?t=1770154804 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Iron Frontier 是一款 roguelike 即时战略卡牌游戏。游戏融合了多种游戏类型的元素，以独特的方式融合了动作、战术和战略，创造了独特的游戏体验。'Plants vs Zombies'与'Age of War'相遇''，'Brotato'增强系统。欢迎回来，指挥官！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131290/extras/9257926122119bc3da7836ed5cfaa0a5.poster.avif?t=1770154804\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131290/extras/9257926122119bc3da7836ed5cfaa0a5.webm?t=1770154804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131290/extras/9257926122119bc3da7836ed5cfaa0a5.mp4?t=1770154804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>防御</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌军正从两侧接近您的阵地。建造基地并尽最大努力保卫它。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>控制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从数十个单位、建筑物和将军中创建你的军队。命令你的部队智胜敌人。使用空袭和其他能力在战场上播下死亡的种子！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过数百种升级和能力提升来增强您的部队。解锁新单位、技术和永久升级，将您的军队变成杀人机器！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>毁灭</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以狡猾的战术和压倒性的火力消灭敌军。创建终极军队，将战场变成死亡地带！不要俘虏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战场上见！</p>",
